Package: primertools
Title: Tools for Reading and Writing PRIMER Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Adam", "Smith", , "anhsmith@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Utility functions for preparing PRIMER-ready input files and for reading common output files produced by PRIMER software (e.g. PERMANOVA results), supporting reproducible workflows that combine PRIMER with downstream analysis and reporting in R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://anhsmith.github.io/primertools/
